      "reviews": [
        {
          "reviewTitle": "AMAZING! But probably not the best for oily skin :(",
          "reviewText": "This product is great! Even as a skin tint, it still gives satisfactory coverage. It adds A LOT, and I mean A LOT of glow to my face. However, to all my oily girls out there, I want to say that this might not be for you, sadly. As I bought it, I thought this product wouldn't give me much of a glow (even though it does say \"Sheer Glow Hydrating Foundation Stick\" \ud83e\udd26\u2640\ufe0f), and I was EXTREMELY wrong. So if you're like me and you have oily skin, please reconsider buying something else, maybe a matte skin tint or foundation, as I have. I hardly use this product anymore as it just makes me even more oily, and I've noticed myself applying setting powder more often throughout the day. However, if you don't have oily skin and want that extra glow, this is totally the product for you. When completely out, there's about 2 inches of product, and the application is SOO smooth. It can be easily brushed into the skin with a foundation brush or just a blender. Its super lightweight to the point I hardly feel it there. The coverage is not much as it is a skintint, but it definitely covers most of my redness. Price-wise, I'd say it is definitely priced the way it is for a reason. The product is really high quality, and the packaging is to die for-so pretty! Hope this helps!",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2026",
          "customer": "Ena",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AHUSIY4YLJ7RR4RR2MSV4RXKDDXA",
