          "reviewTitle": "Glowy like a highlighter but good",
          "reviewText": "Very nice. Just know that it is very thin so if you want full coverage this isn\u2019t it. You can wear it on its own or layer foundation or tinted moisturizer on top. It has a glowy sheen. Very pretty. Def put moisturizer on first IF you have dry skin like me.",
