        {
          "reviewTitle": "Gorgeous glowing skin tint.",
          "reviewText": "Gorgeous makeup. Gives a beautiful radiant finish. One of my favorite new makeup products this past year. I read that some ppl think it\u2019s more highlighter than foundation, but I don\u2019t agree. I use a beauty blender to blend and it\u2019s flawless on my skin. However, this isn\u2019t a traditional foundation, it\u2019s a skin tint. Leaves beautiful luminous finish. If I want a more matte finish, I apply this first then use with a matte foundation. (Chanel le tent velvet is gorgeous with this product.) I bought #3 fair with neutral undertones. I do think it\u2019s slightly warm for neutral color, but I have slightly warm undertones, so it is a perfect color for me.",
